Class ElementParser

java.lang.Object
sweng.campusbirdsguide.xml.utils.ElementParser
Direct Known Subclasses:
AudioParser, CircleParser, ImageParser, LineParser, RectangleParser, TextParser, VideoParser
public abstract class ElementParser extends Object
ElementParser is an abstract class which provides base methods and constants to parse elements from presentaton.
